   <text>
      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> TRANQUILLO CREMONA Silenzio amoroso
                                      Silence d'amoreaux
                                      Stille Liebe 
                                      Silent Love</s>
            </p>
            <p rend="writing-mode(vertical-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Proprietà artistica riservata - N 141</s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>Silenzio amoroso</head>
               <figDesc> Coppia di inammorati all' interno di un ovale
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            Modena lì 2/7 - 1917 - </s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p type="retro">
                     <lb/>            Oliva carisfima, <lb/>            un pungente desiderio di vivere con te, di averti <lb/>            sempre costantemente vicina a me, mi stringe a - <lb/>            maramente l'animo e mi fa soffrire<lb/>            quando, quando avremo pace? Non so, <lb/>            non vedo la fine dei tormenti insani e dei <lb/>            miei, non so più sperare, più, più. <lb/>            Il tuo tenero amore mi dà le vertigini del senti - <lb/>            mento, ma non la felicità presente.<lb/>            Il bisogno offerto da te, dei tuoi baci, delle <lb/>            tue carezze, niente altro c'è al mondo che posfa <lb/>            completarmi e vivo scontento. </p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <lb/>
                  <signed>
                     <persName>
                        <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                     </persName>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 110 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
